 Mohanlal is a cameraman of international repute   
 having served with such names as Reuters and BBC. 
 Having been away from homeland for a while,       
 Mohanlal drops in at kerala on an assignment      
 where he gets to meet Amala Paul.Amala Paul works 
 as a senior editor at Bharath Vision telivision   
 channel and Mohanlal and Amala Paul have a story  
 to tell on their own.Mohanlal shares camaraderie 
 with Biju Menon who happens to be his best     
 buddy as well as the head of a local telivison 
 channel that is struggling to stand on its own   
 Despite their differences after their early       
 breakup,Mohanlal and Amala Paul are forced by    
 Circumstances to work together again for a secret 
